original_title: Jimi Hendrix: Blue Wild Angel - Live At The Isle Of Wight
overview: Jimi Hendrix's last UK performance was a memorable one, taking place at England's answer to Woodstock: the Isle of Wight rock festival. This video features the entire set, which includes incendiary versions of 'All Along the Watchtower', 'Voodoo Chile' and 'Message To Love'.
title: Jimi Hendrix: Blue Wild Angel - Live At The Isle Of Wight
